    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043860/extras/893fc796a75652d12328675beb46ab56.poster.avif?t=1756139801\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043860/extras/893fc796a75652d12328675beb46ab56.webm?t=1756139801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043860/extras/893fc796a75652d12328675beb46ab56.mp4?t=1756139801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《数据记痕》是一款单人解谜冒险游戏，拥有标志性的Vaporwave视觉美学风格。当克洛伊答应参与父亲的实验后，意外被困进了一台正在崩溃的家庭电脑中。在父亲努力设法营救的同时，她必须小心翼翼探索文件和程序，解开逻辑谜题，同时设法抢在持续进行的系统崩溃之前，不断向前，寻找出路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏亮点</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   一段交织回忆与情感的故事缓缓展开。克洛伊在翻阅旧相册与调查废弃项目的过程中，逐步揭开一段神秘的家族往事。他们是谁？曾经历过什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   在这个诡异的数字世界中，克洛伊需要遵循父亲的指引。尽管他在尽全力救你脱困，但只能偶尔与你取得联系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   游戏拥有极具特色的 Vaporwave 视觉风格，粉色的落日洒满无尽的地平线，棱角分明的几何景观不断延伸，复古街机的光影在空气中若隐若现，营造出迷离而诡异的氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   谜题与探索相辅相成，挑战与发现并存：在二进制与十六进制中抽丝剥茧，用颜色代码组合出正确的钥匙，收集并正确使用道具。唯有学会像机器那样思考，才能在崩溃的系统中生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043860/extras/02e8ca20830490700c0f6ea3dd562930.poster.avif?t=1756139801\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043860/extras/02e8ca20830490700c0f6ea3dd562930.webm?t=1756139801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043860/extras/02e8ca20830490700c0f6ea3dd562930.mp4?t=1756139801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逃离不断崩溃的数字世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个神秘的电脑世界正逐步崩溃，一切都显得支离破碎：损坏的文件、缺失的数据……你必须始终抢先一步解开谜题，在剧情推进的过程中不断前行，而你的父亲也在拼尽全力将你拯救出来。这个世界充满隐藏的规律与线索：从颜色代码到二进制片段，从逻辑链条到秘密信息。唯有敏锐的思维与细致的观察，才能带你逃出生天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043860/extras/879cb6669cb0b4a554a35b537b58cf61.poster.avif?t=1756139801\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043860/extras/879cb6669cb0b4a554a35b537b58cf61.webm?t=1756139801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043860/extras/879cb6669cb0b4a554a35b537b58cf61.mp4?t=1756139801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>揭开机器的真相</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这台电脑原本属于谁？他们发生了什么？这个世界究竟是如何构建起来的？又为何正在分崩离析？探索破碎的记忆，穿行于被遗忘的相册与废弃的游戏原型之间，直到拼凑出真相——这是你唯一的出路。</p>",
